1116
01:36:34,000 --> 01:36:37,000
That's not what Aleosha intended to do.

1117
01:36:37,000 --> 01:36:39,000
But that's the way it's experienced.

1118
01:36:39,000 --> 01:36:40,000
And so there's this way.

1119
01:36:40,000 --> 01:36:42,000
He comes to recognize, oh my God,

1120
01:36:42,000 --> 01:36:48,000
like what I'm supposed to do is love people in Dostoevsky's view of things.

1121
01:36:48,000 --> 01:36:51,000
