1145
01:38:08,000 --> 01:38:10,000
that others were doing in the past?

1146
01:38:10,000 --> 01:38:12,000
So it's not simple.

1147
01:38:12,000 --> 01:38:19,000
Once you see that there's evil being done, that it's easy to fix.

1148
01:38:19,000 --> 01:38:27,000
No, in our society, there's something about our human nature

1149
01:38:27,000 --> 01:38:33,000
that just too easily stops listening to the world, to empathizing with the world.

1150
01:38:33,000 --> 01:38:35,000
And we label things as evil.

1151
01:38:35,000 --> 01:38:37,000
This is through human history.

1152
01:38:37,000 --> 01:38:38,000
This is evil.

1153
01:38:38,000 --> 01:38:40,000
You mentioned tribes.

1154
01:38:40,000 --> 01:38:42,000
This religious belief is evil.

1155
01:38:42,000 --> 01:38:45,000
