1182
01:40:18,000 --> 01:40:25,000
And so it's sort of required that we're going to have to be empathetic,

1183
01:40:25,000 --> 01:40:32,000
that we're going to have to recognize that others are dealing with that just as we are.

1184
01:40:32,000 --> 01:40:34,000
